Package com.ibm.team.repository.common.query

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDataField
    Data fields represent descriptions of the columnar data returned from data queries.
    IDataQuery
    a data query is a type of query used for retrieving fields of related items, or values computed by aggregate or scalar functions.
    IDataQueryPage
    Represents the definition of a query page for data queries.
    IDataRow
    Represents a row of data from a data query result.
    IDataRow.Factory  
    IDataTypes
    Enumeration interface that defines int constants corresponding to all data query field types.
    IItemQuery
    an item query is a type of query used for retrieving the handles of all items matching a set of filter criteria.
    IItemQueryPage
    Represents the definition of a query page for item queries.
    IQuery
    Represents a structured query over items in the Jazz repository.
    IQueryGenerationOptions
    Provides support for passing a small set of options to the SQL generator.
    IQueryPage
    Represents the abstract definition of a paged query result.
    IQueryResult  
    IScored  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IQuery.Factory<T extends IQuery,Q extends IQueryModel>
    internal use only
    IQueryGenerationOptions.Factory
    Factory class for creating instances of IQueryGenerationOptions.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    IDataQuery.RedactionRule
    Note that no redaction will occur if the server is not configured for redaction.
    IQueryGenerationOptions.BaselinePattern
    Used to specify the pattern that should be used within the SQL generated for a query that ie executed in the context of a baseline.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    QueryException
